---
title: Sticky Chili-Garlic Chicken and Green Beans with Crispy Shallot Rice
description: Get ready for everyone's favourite Canadian-Chinese takeout dish made at home! You won't have to sacrifice convenience for flavour, since tonight's recipe comes together in just a few simple steps. Chicken is cooked in a sweet and savoury sauce with crunch-tastic crispy shallots sprinkled over top!
